<h2>What's New in 1.9.18</h2>  <ul><li><strong>Monthly overage spend at a glance</strong> — AIQuota now shows how much Codex bonus credit spend and Claude extra usage you have used this month.</li> <li><strong>Clearer credit details</strong> — Codex balances are shown as dollars, separate from the monthly amount spent after limits.</li> <li><strong>Cleaner overage styling</strong> — Spent rows are highlighted in amber across the popover and widgets, with red reserved for true limit or cap states.</li> <li><strong>Helpful spend context</strong> — Hover over the Spent row in the menu bar popover to see how the monthly amount is calculated and when it applies.</li></ul> <img src="https://github.com/niederme/ai-quota/releases/download/v1.9.18/AIQuota-1.9.18.png" alt="AIQuota 1.9.18" width="600">
